        {
            "title": "當地儲能需求上升 中國企業考慮在印度建電池廠",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 中國遠景科技集團正考慮在印度建一座電池製造廠，以把握當地政府推動電網升級以適應更多可再生能源的機遇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">遠景的全球合同負責人Suman Nag在接受採訪時表示，一旦這個新興市場發展起來，公司希望通過一座年產5吉瓦時、投資3400萬美元的電池製造廠進軍該領域。該項目將從中國採購電池組，並在本地建設機架和軟件基礎設施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「作為一家中國企業的印度子公司，我們很樂意進行本地化生產，」 Nag說。「僅僅把設備過賬並計入銷售額，並不能為我們在印度的公司增加任何價值」。他補充道，預計將在18個月內根據市場情況做出決定。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e3710df4-16ff-3a9a-bc45-67147a49ce17-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wfwMSMjnpBTINgvOZcXF.w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d731801265b402609868d293c1e4df45\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度加快可再生能源裝機規模的能力受到儲能系統不足的制約，而儲能系統對於穩定電力傳輸至關重要。這導致電網運營商不得不限制過剩的太陽能發電量——原本可以用來在白天給電池充電，並在夜間提供可靠電力。雖然該國目前的電池儲能容量不足1吉瓦，但投資者對巨大的成長潛力很感興趣，預計到2032年將達到46吉瓦。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Chinese Firm Mulls India Battery Plant as Storage Demand Rises</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%84%B2%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%BB%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%B1%A0%E5%BB%A0-075525119.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 18:55:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財政大臣的預算案掃清了英國央行重啟降息的障礙",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/REbhwZfgPWed7bjYgoKtUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/49b870440e00602c28e535ec9d22614e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 儘管英國財政大臣蕾切爾·里夫斯的預算案在抗擊通膨方面不如幾周前預期那般強勁，但她為英國央行下月重啟降息鋪平了道路。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位財政大臣表示，其財政計畫將緩解英國通膨困境 —— 該國物價漲幅仍居七國集團之首。預算責任辦公室預計，里夫斯的政策組合（包括凍結鐵路票價、延長燃油稅減免政策一年、降低家庭能源賬單等措施）將在明年第二季度使通膨率降低多達0.5個百分點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管預算案公佈後交易員幾乎認定12月18日會議將降息，但經濟學家提醒，英國央行關注的長期前景更為複雜。這將限制更快速降息周期的操作空間。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-72817ea3-d720-36e4-96ed-e701c74f5c2a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"688\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MgWZInXmZXDxsoBwHxwiAw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2beee8b966783a2da630bb3fbddfc34a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">里夫斯在最後一刻改變主意之前考慮提交的預算案 —— 該方案將提高所得稅稅率，這將違背競選承諾 —— 原本被認為更有可能遏制頑固的高通膨壓力。但她最終推遲了幾乎所有增稅措施，批准了最低工資的再次上調，甚至在預測期的前幾年放寬了政策。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">景順全球研究主管Benjamin Jones表示，「鑒於所得稅稅率維持不變，該預算案的緊縮力度略低於部分人士的擔憂。但其仍具通縮效應，加之近期通膨壓力已顯緩解，英國央行有望重啟降息周期。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Reeves Lifts Hurdle to Bank of England Cut With Budget Moves (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%8E%83%E6%B8%85%E4%BA%86%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%9C%E7%A4%99-092326442.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 18:10:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
